            <lg xml:id="TK1042">
<l>iṉmai yeṉavoru pāvi maṟumaiyu </l>
<l>mimmaiyu miṉṟi varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When cruel poverty comes on, it deprives one of both the present and future (bliss).</l>
            </lg>
